400 PRINT "WHAT A DODECAHEDRON IS, ASK SOMEONE)"
405 PRINT
410 PRINT "     HAZARDS:"
415 PRINT " BOTTOMLESS PITS - TWO ROOMS HAVE BOTTOMLESS PITS IN THEM"
